item.title: Woodcutting?
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Replace yours with mine.

public void Woodcutting() { if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("choptree")) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP((125*playerLevel[8]), 8); //sendMessage("You chop down the tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgpere]); } if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopoak") && playerLevel[8] >= 15) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP((250*playerLevel[8]),8); //sendMessage("You chop down the oak tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgphere]); } else if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopoak") && playerLevel[8] < 15) { sendMessage("You must be at least level 15 to chop down this tree!"); } if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopwillow") && playerLevel[8] >= 30) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP((500*playerLevel[8]),8); //sendMessage("You chop down the willow tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgphere]); } else if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopwillow") && playerLevel[8] < 30) { sendMessage("You must be at least level 30 to chop down this tree!"); } if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopmaple") && playerLevel[8] >= 45) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP((1000*playerLevel[8]),8); //sendMessage("You chop down the maple tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgphere]); } else if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopmaple") && playerLevel[8] < 45) { sendMessage("You must be at least level 45 to chop down this tree!"); } if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopyew") && playerLevel[8] >= 60) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP((2500*playerLevel[8]),8); //sendMessage("You chop down the yew tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgphere]); } else if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopyew") && playerLevel[8] < 60) { sendMessage("You must be at least level 60 to chop down this tree!"); } if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopmagic") && playerLevel[8] >= 75) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP((5000*playerLevel[8]),8); //sendMessage("You chop down the magic tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgphere]); } else if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopmagic") && playerLevel[8] < 75) { sendMessage("You must be at least level 75 to chop down this tree!"); } if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chophollow") && playerLevel[8] >= 45) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP(100,8); //sendMessage("You chop down the hollow tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgphere]); } else if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chophollow") && playerLevel[8] < 45) { sendMessage("You must be at least level 45 to chop down this tree!"); } if (actionName.equalsIgnoreCase("chopachey")) { if (actionTimer == 0) addSkillXP(25, 8); //sendMessage("You chop down the achey tree!"); addItem(995, [amountofgphere]); } }

All you have to do now is replace the “0” in the actiontimer to a higher number.

		}
